=========
Changelog
=========

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on `Keep a Changelog <https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/>`_,
and this project adheres to `Semantic Versioning <https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html>`_.


`0.5.0`_ (2019-11-25)
---------------------
.. _0.5.0: https://github.com/prashnts/pybloomfiltermmap3/releases/tag/0.5.0

Changes
^^^^^^^
- Add support for read-only Bloom filter files (`@mizvyt <mizvyt_>`_)
- Add customization of hash seeds for hashing algorithms (`@mizvyt <mizvyt_>`_)
- Drop Python < 3.5 support (`@mizvyt <mizvyt_>`_)

Fixes
^^^^^
- Fix installation errors due to missing Cython deps, should now be fixed (`@mizvyt <mizvyt_>`_)


`0.4.19`_ (2019-10-11)
----------------------
.. _0.4.19: https://pypi.org/project/pybloomfiltermmap3/0.4.19

Changes
^^^^^^^
- Ensure that filename is encoded in :meth:`~pybloomfilter.BloomFilter.copy_template` (`@gonzalezzfelipe <gonzalezzfelipe_>`_)


`0.4.18`_ (2019-10-08)
----------------------
.. _0.4.18: https://pypi.org/project/pybloomfiltermmap3/0.4.18

Fixes
^^^^^
- Fix missing Cython dependency in setup.py (`@mizvyt <mizvyt_>`_)


`0.4.17`_ (2019-08-25)
----------------------
.. _0.4.17: https://pypi.org/project/pybloomfiltermmap3/0.4.17

Fixes
^^^^^
- PyPi wants ``long_description`` and its type (`@prashnts <prashnts_>`_)


`0.4.16`_ (2019-08-25)
----------------------
.. _0.4.16: https://pypi.org/project/pybloomfiltermmap3/0.4.16

Fixes
^^^^^
- Fix read / write of base64 encoded filter files (`@gaetano-guerriero <gaetano-guerriero_>`_)


`0.4.15`_ (2019-04-09)
----------------------
.. _0.4.15: https://pypi.org/project/pybloomfiltermmap3/0.4.15

Changes
^^^^^^^
- Remove Python 2 support, add Python 3 support (`@prashnts <prashnts_>`_)


Previous Versions
-----------------

See Python 2 `pybloomfiltermmap CHANGELOG <https://github.com/axiak/pybloomfiltermmap/blob/master/CHANGELOG>`_.


